issue.title: Bump webmock from 3.6.0 to 3.7.2 in /megafono.host
issue.body:
Bumps [webmock](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock) from 3.6.0 to 3.7.2.
Changelog *Sourced from [webmock's changelog](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md).* > ## 3.7.2 > > * Fixed handling of non UTF-8 encoded urls > > Thanks to [Rafael França](https://github.com/rafaelfranca) > > * Fixed "shadowing outer local variable" warning > > Thanks to [y-yagi](https://github.com/y-yagi) > > ## 3.7.1 > > * Fixed Async::HTTP::Client adapter code to not cause Ruby warning > > Thanks to [y-yagi](https://github.com/y-yagi) > > ## 3.7.0 > > * Support for Async::HTTP::Client > > Thanks to [Andriy Yanko](https://github.com/ayanko) > > ## 3.6.2 > > * Fixed Patron adapter to handle HTTP/2 status line. > > Thanks to [Fábio D. Batista](https://github.com/fabiob) > > ## 3.6.1 > > * Fixed issue with matching Addressable::Template without a period in the domain > > Thanks to [Eike Send](https://github.com/eikes) > > * Support for `write_timeout` in Net::HTTP > > Thanks to [Claudio Poli](https://github.com/masterkain) > > * Fixed issue with handling urls with ":80" or ":443" in the path. > > Thanks to [Csaba Apagyi](https://github.com/thisismydesign) for reporting and to [Frederick Cheung](https://github.com/fcheung) for fixing the issue.
Commits - [`2a15b26`](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/commit/2a15b268e6bbb581406c42410e0d28406ce0d842) Version 3.7.2 - [`6c2f336`](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/commit/6c2f3366a6e6c829f0435941ca7d2c114dbb6ea7) Merge pull request [#843](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/bblimke/webmock/issues/843) from rafaelfranca/rm-fix-encoding-problem-after-832 - [`5c3dcf8`](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/commit/5c3dcf810936611368cd9cc4f5f4539d19247ca3) Change encoding only when generating the strings - [`ab77792`](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/commit/ab77792efb8790f3139cccd761f02a78d141f571) Remove unecessary encoding change - [`0351cdf`](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/commit/0351cdf7805a506acd35624b2de030c1dc5bb61f) Do not try to gsub on incompatible encoding - [`5b1754b`](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/commit/5b1754b3a6106cbfa58f9386b04e47c38b0f84a6) Merge pull request [#835](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/bblimke/webmock/issues/835) from tadassce/em-http-timeout - [`f38c47e`](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/commit/f38c47e90df6584732781f33e53941e74086f565) Fix EM HTTP request adapter's timeout class - [`8b0d6a5`](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/commit/8b0d6a5926d0b70acd835a75c4cc4590fd6b1349) Version 3.7.1 - [`564cbb5`](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/commit/564cbb5156b2b4c7303b30cbe62c0d0efb861251) Merge pull request [#842](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/bblimke/webmock/issues/842) from y-yagi/fix_ruby_warning - [`63a6376`](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/commit/63a6376749ffe38c50f0dacfb214fde5f2400245) Fix "warning: shadowing outer local variable - v" - Additional commits viewable in [compare view](https://github.com/bblimke/webmock/compare/v3.6.0...v3.7.2)
